            <p class="gallery-para-animate2 body-text">The Clinton campaign followed suit, though Bierut and his team at Pentagram strove to make Clinton’s branding less about exuding familiarity and experience more about being approachable.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="gallery-logo-2">
            <p class="gallery-para-animate3 body-text">Designed by Maria Arenas, the Alexandria Ocasio’s campaign was fresh, stylish, and modern. Arenas’ work combined great photography with striking typography, using the simple concept of complimentary colours (#EFCA2D for the yellow and #464675 for the purple) to devise a powerful, shareable set of graphics.</p>
